verbose_text: In this regard, it should be noted that SDF-1 is not only a chemotactic factor, but also promotes chondrocyte hypertrophy through its interaction with C-X-C chemokine receptor type 4 (CXCR4) on chondrocytes and upregulation of RUNX2 expression, which is part of the cascade of endochondral ossification in the growth plate XREF_BIBR.
